OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and bright start for
OL,6,Feastern parts, with some sunny
OL,7,Fintervals, then clouding over through
OL,8,Fthe morning. Cloudier in the west,
OL,9,Fespecially over hills, with the chance
OL,10,Fof the odd light isolated shower.
OL,11,FLight winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloud soon clearing this
OL,14,Fevening, with sunny spells developing,
OL,15,Fespecially across the east. Cloud
OL,16,Fthickening after dark, with outbreaks
OL,17,Fof mostly light rain spreading
OL,18,Fnorthwest through the early hours.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
